    height: 135
  isDragging: 0
  isSelected: 0
  sentence:
    characterName: Dr. Asclepio
    text: "Yes. It may feel scary at first, but a therapist is there to listen, not
      judge. And they\u2019ll work with you at your pace. You don\u2019t have to
      do this alone."
